text: Artyukhovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Aydaralinsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 52 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Sterlibashevo, 2 km from Aydarali. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Artyukhovka
